displayProperties.name: Warped Rachis
displayProperties.description: Apply this shader to change the color of your gear.

displayProperties.name: Shed Carapace
displayProperties.description: Apply this shader to change the color of your gear.

displayProperties.name: Cursed Thrall
displayProperties.description: After defeating a target with a melee attack, final blows with this weapon cause targets to explode for a short duration.

displayProperties.name: Necrochasm Catalyst
displayProperties.description:
Upgrades this weapon to a Masterwork. Once upgraded, the weapon will obtain enhanced capabilities, such as increased stats and/or additional perks.

Defeat targets using this weapon to unlock this upgrade.

displayProperties.name: Desperation
displayProperties.description: Reloading after a precision final blow or a final blow with a Cursed Thrall explosion increases your rate of fire and improves stability and aim assist.

displayProperties.name: Arrowhead Brake
displayProperties.description:
Lightly vented barrel.
  •  Greatly controls recoil
  •  Increases handling speed

displayProperties.name: Hand-Laid Stock
displayProperties.description:
This weapon is optimized for recoil control.
  •  Increases stability

displayProperties.name: Default Effect
displayProperties.description: Use default transmat effects when arriving in a location or reviving.

displayProperties.name: Empty Catalyst Socket
displayProperties.description:
An Exotic catalyst can be inserted into this socket.

Check the Exotic catalysts section in Triumphs to learn where the catalyst can be obtained.

displayProperties.name: Ricochet Rounds
displayProperties.description:
Rounds ricochet off hard surfaces. 
  •  Increases stability 
  •  Slightly increases range

displayProperties.name: Kill Tracker
displayProperties.description: This weapon tracks the number of enemies you defeated with it.

displayProperties.name: Cursebringer
displayProperties.description: Precision final blows with this weapon trigger a Cursed Thrall explosion. Final blows with Cursed Thrall explosions refill the magazine.

displayProperties.name: Default Shader
displayProperties.description: Restores your gear to its default colors.
